  "detailed_description": "<strong>Joseon-Fantasy Detective Visual Novel</strong><br><br>---<br><strong>1. Episode Composition</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/70c58e16ca1bc4f097ad080817ae1c3a.avif?t=1724590325\" width=200 height=262 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/4dd453c4a510bf6089b46d3ac5e6b25d.avif?t=1724590325\" width=200 height=262 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/51f1b9607a4ccc9d784ab8e867841f51.avif?t=1724590325\" width=200 height=262 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/564d1e60bf3873b23f845218c7ef7b7b.avif?t=1724590325\" width=200 height=262 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/8aafbcc32e96c01ce85c9bbb9f0639be.avif?t=1724590325\" width=200 height=262 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/538c752ccd4621b9c274b6bbe8f2de35.avif?t=1724590325\" width=200 height=262 /></span><br><br>- A monster-related murder case unfolds in the eight provinces of Joseon. Play 6 detective episodes based on local korean folklore and uncover the truth behind the cases.<br>- Each episode has 3 to 4 multiple endings.<br><br>---<br><strong>2. Investigation</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/c08ccfbf64c6762ce9b0b65e4bcf87b1.avif?t=1724590325\" width=620 height=220 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/dd1ea5b4db612c887501bae8e57c14ee.avif?t=1724590325\" width=620 height=220 /></span><br><br>- Investigate the scene of the incident and collect clues necessary to solve the case.<br>- Talk to NPC characters to obtain testimonies.<br>- Use the clues and testimonies to make deductions.<br>- Combine the deductions to reach a conclusion of the case. There is only one truth among many conclusions.<br><br>---<br><strong>3. Confrontation</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/31d3fa1732398a0ed8c155c83298e37e.avif?t=1724590325\" width=620 height=400 /></span><br><br>- If you correctly identify the culprit or the monster behind the incident, you will engage in a one-on-one logical battle.<br>- Expose the villain's lies and land a strike by presenting clues.<br><br>---<br><strong>4. Character Chemistry</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/0ab4d0de03c17e91deb84f1651b6c0af.avif?t=1724590325\" width=620 height=330 /></span><br><br>- The player embarks on a journey with colleague Jo Gun-Gwan from the perspective of Jeong Do-sa.<br>- Experience the story of Jeong Do-sa and Jo Gun-Gwan growing together as they encounter various cases.<br>- If you need hints during gameplay, you can always consult Jo Gun-Gwan.<br><br>---<br><strong>5. NPCs</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/ac82a02a27c75c09c759e5f049601c1d.avif?t=1724590325\" width=300 height=300 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/c6e6ba75f940ee2609d9274ef32da835.avif?t=1724590325\" width=300 height=300 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/515198281e8d319d4e9a221d5786f84a.avif?t=1724590325\" width=300 height=300 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329060/extras/7731473843cb30c7b0840cefd45e095e.avif?t=1724590325\" width=300 height=300 /></span><br><br>- Talk with over 30 characters in 6 episodes.<br>- Monsters, Monks, and Villagers all have their say in the weird case that is going on.",
